These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite
Movie-Genre: mystery, satire
Sport: rowing, cricket
Transport: motorbike, bus
1. Transport:bus is on the left or right of Sport:cricket##3
2. Beverage:sprite is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:satire == Beverage:mirinda##1
4. Transport:bus is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | sprite   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | mystery   |
| Sport         | cricket | rowing |
| Transport     | motorbike | bus    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: peach, cherry
Movie-Genre: crime, mystery
Pet: goldfish, hedgehog
Transport: trike, car
1. Pet:hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:crime == Transport:car##1
3. Food:cherry is on the right of Movie-Genre:mystery##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peach     | cherry |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | crime  |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | goldfish     |
| Transport     | trike   | car    |

 #################################
 
