.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Job: fisherman, entrepreneur
Nationality: thai, french
Pet: fish, frog
Sport: tennis, lacrosse
1. Sport:lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:french is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:entrepreneur == Nationality:thai##1
4. Pet:fish is on the left of Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | fisherman    |
| Nationality   | thai       | french |
| Pet           | fish         | frog    |
| Sport         | tennis    | lacrosse   |

